<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ec65f63-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s286r"><num value="286r">§ 286r.</num><heading> United States participation in special drawing account</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of article XXI(b) of the Articles of Agreement of the Fund shall have full force and effect in the United States and its territories and possessions when the United States becomes a participant in the special drawing account.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8ec65f64-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/349/s7">Pub. L. 90–349, § 7</ref>, <date date="1968-06-19">June 19, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/189">82 Stat. 189</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/94/564/s5/4">Pub. L. 94–564, § 5(4)</ref>, <date date="1976-10-19">Oct. 19, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2661">90 Stat. 2661</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id8ec65f65-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id8ec65f66-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id8ec65f67-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as part of <ref href="/us/act/1945-07-31/ch339">act July 31, 1945, ch. 339</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/59/512">59 Stat. 512</ref>, known as the Bretton Woods Agreement Act, which comprises this subchapter.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id8ec65f68-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1976—<ref href="/us/pl/94/564">Pub. L. 94–564</ref> substituted “article XXI(b)” for “article XXVII(b)”.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id8ec65f69-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="id8ec65f6a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1976 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment effective <date date="1978-04-01">Apr. 1, 1978</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/94/564/s9">section 9 of Pub. L. 94–564</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s286a">section 286a of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
